{
  "page": {
    "name": "知识库编辑",
    "parent": "bot/agent/knowledge_base/list",
    "type": 2,
    "sort": 10,
    "auth": [
      {
        "key": "bot/agent/knowledge_base/create",
        "name": "知识库新增",
        "query": {
          "id": "empty"
        }
      },
      {
        "key": "bot/agent/knowledge_base/update",
        "name": "知识库编辑",
        "query": {
          "id": "required"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "layout": {
    "type": "container",
    "children": {
      "page-main": {
        "type": "main",
        "className": "p-0",
        "children": {
          "tabs-row": {
            "type": "container",
            "className": "mb-4"
          },
          "dialog-shell": {
            "type": "container",
            "className": "w-full"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "nodes": {
    "tabs-row": [
      {
        "type": "nav-tab",
        "meta": {
          "target": "state.currentTab",
          "variant": "line",
          "tabs": [
            {
              "label": "基础配置",
              "value": "basic"
            },
            {
              "label": "索引配置",
              "value": "index"
            },
            {
              "label": "检索配置",
              "value": "retrieval"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "dialog-shell": [
      {
        "type": "form-select",
        "value": "form.cate_id",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": {
          "model": "bot.agent.NewKnowledgeCateModel",
          "filters": {
            "status": 1
          },
          "order": "sort asc,id asc"
        },
        "validate": [
          {
            "type": "required",
            "message": "知识库分类不能为空。"
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "basic",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[260px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "placeholder": "例如：企业业务知识库",
        "value": "form.name",
        "mode": "form",
        "validate": [
          {
            "type": "required",
            "message": "知识库名称不能为空。"
          },
          {
            "type": "model",
            "except": "$form.id",
            "message": "该分类下知识库名称已存在。"
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "basic"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-select",
        "name": "文档解析服务",
        "placeholder": "可选，选择 MinerU 服务",
        "value": "form.parser_service_id",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": {
          "type": "service",
          "service": "bot.agent.setting.OptionService.LoadKnowledgeParserServices"
        },
        "info": "可选。选择后，后续 PDF、Office、图片等复杂文件可以使用该服务解析；不选择则只使用本地文本解析和已有兜底能力。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "index",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[360px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-number",
        "name": "节点最大长度",
        "value": "form.node_max_length",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "单个知识节点的大致最大字符数。系统会优先按文档目录、标题、页面、段落、表格等结构生成节点；如果某个节点过长，再按这个长度做保底拆分，默认 800。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "index",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[160px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-number",
        "name": "长节点重叠",
        "value": "form.node_split_overlap",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "长节点被保底拆分时，相邻节点重复保留的字符数，用于避免关键信息落在切分边界导致检索不到，默认 120。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "index",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[160px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-select",
        "name": "向量能力",
        "placeholder": "可选，选择 embeddings 类型能力",
        "value": "form.embedding_power_id",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": {
          "type": "service",
          "service": "bot.agent.setting.OptionService.LoadEmbeddingPowers"
        },
        "info": "可选。选择 embeddings 类型能力后，会额外生成语义向量，用于相似内容检索；不选择则使用全文检索、目录图谱和智能规划检索。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "index",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[360px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-radio",
        "name": "概念图谱",
        "value": "form.concept_graph_enabled",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": [
          {"id": 1, "value": "启用"},
          {"id": 2, "value": "禁用"}
        ],
        "info": "启用后，索引阶段每篇文档会由 LLM 抽取概念和关系（includes、depends_on 等语义边），形成语义关系网络。检索时可通过图谱扩展找到更相关的文档，适合需要深度语义理解的场景。如只做关键词/语义检索，不需要关联发现，可关闭。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "index",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[240px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-select",
        "name": "索引模型",
        "placeholder": "可选，选择文本类型能力",
        "value": "form.index_power_id",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": {
          "type": "service",
          "service": "bot.agent.setting.OptionService.LoadTextPowers"
        },
        "info": "启用概念图谱时需要选择索引模型，用于文档摘要、目录摘要、检索规划和概念关系抽取。如不启用概念图谱且仅做关键词/语义检索，则无需选择。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "index",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[360px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-number",
        "name": "检索数量",
        "value": "form.retrieve_limit",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "智能体每次从该知识库最多取多少条候选知识。数量越多覆盖面越大，但更容易混入弱相关内容，默认 5。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "retrieval",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[160px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-number",
        "name": "最大字数",
        "value": "form.max_context_chars",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "最多注入到智能体上下文里的知识内容总字数。太小可能信息不足，太大可能增加成本并干扰重点，默认 6000。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "retrieval",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[180px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-number",
        "name": "匹配阈值",
        "value": "form.score_threshold",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "用于过滤低相关知识的最低匹配要求。阈值越高结果越严格；阈值越低覆盖更多但可能混入噪声，默认 0.35。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "retrieval",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[160px]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-number",
        "name": "扩展层数",
        "value": "form.graph_depth",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "命中某个目录或知识点后，继续向父级和子级目录扩展几层关联内容。默认 1 层；2 层适合复杂关联问题，但可能带入更多噪声。",
        "meta": {
          "formLayout": "horizontal",
          "tab": "retrieval",
          "controlClassName": "max-w-[160px]"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "form": {
      "id": 0,
      "cate_id": 1,
      "name": "",
      "parser_service_id": "",
      "index_power_id": "",
      "embedding_power_id": "",
      "concept_graph_enabled": 1,
      "node_max_length": 800,
      "node_split_overlap": 120,
      "retrieve_limit": 5,
      "score_threshold": 0.35,
      "max_context_chars": 6000,
      "graph_depth": 1,
      "status": 1,
      "sort": 100
    }
  },
  "state": {
    "currentTab": "basic"
  },
  "action": {
    "submit": {
      "type": "save",
      "params": "form",
      "before": {
        "type": "service",
        "use": "bot.agent.knowledge.KnowledgeHook.BeforeSaveKnowledgeBase"
      },
      "after": {
        "type": "service",
        "use": "bot.agent.knowledge.KnowledgeHook.AfterSaveKnowledgeBase"
      }
    }
  }
}
